overview: A nice little appetizer before the Uncensored Rumble that will follow the next day. A lot of new faces present and some seem to have convinced WSU officials (Bale, D'Milo, Garrett, Hayden, Malone). Hendrix and Kaye also made a good impression, but I guess WSU and its limited number of shows do not have 50,000 seats in their roster. 09.08.2013
title: WSU Secret Show
